OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FThousands of people have been left
OL,7,Fscrambling to rearrange travel plans
OL,8,Fas the impact of a six-hour closure of
OL,9,FBirmingham Airport's runway continues
OL,10,Fto rumble on.
OL,12,FThe runway reopened late yesterday
OL,13,Fevening (6th August), after a light
OL,14,Faircraft made an emergency landing
OL,15,Fwhich forced a shut down of planned
OL,16,Fflights in and out.
OL,18,FWest Midlands Police has confirmed
OL,19,Fthat a small aircraft was involved in
OL,20,Fan emergency landing yesterday, around
OL,21,F1:40pm.
