OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FOne person was reported to have minor
OL,7,Finjuries. The Air Accidents
OL,8,FInvestigation Branch has started an
OL,9,Finvestigation into the incident.
OL,11,FVideo footage shows the moment the
OL,12,Fplane had to make an emergency landing
OL,13,Fon the runway (credit: Harley
OL,14,FKillingsworth)
OL,16,FThe disruption left many unsure of
OL,17,Fwhat to do next, or how to get help.
OL,18,FSome passengers have told ITV News
OL,19,FCentral reporter Ravneet Nandra about
OL,20,Fthe delays they faced.
