OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,F"They told me "yes" it was still
OL,7,Fplanned as normal. I explained that
OL,8,Fthere had been a crash at Birmingham
OL,9,Fairport ... that the runway was closed
OL,10,Ffrom landing or taking off and they
OL,11,Fnever knew nothing. It wasn't till I
OL,12,Fshowed them the information ... that
OL,13,Fthey then said they had to speak to
OL,14,Ftheir supervisor.
OL,16,F"We should have boarded 5:30pm
OL,17,F(English time), we never got on a
OL,18,Fplane till 7:50pm (Spanish time). We
OL,19,Fwere then sat on the plane for at
OL,20,Fleast another hour before there was an
OL,21,Fannouncement.
