OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,F"We managed to take off and land back
OL,7,Fin Birmingham just after 11pm last
OL,8,Fnight .... We were also left sat on a
OL,9,Fbus for 45 minutes outside the
OL,10,Faircraft with no explanation of what
OL,11,Fwas happening or any complimentary
OL,12,Fbottles of water offered, considering
OL,13,Fwe were sat there a long time in
OL,14,Fblazing heat (32 degrees).
OL,16,F"Young babies on that bus too who were
OL,17,Fcrying in distress"
