OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FSally said "There were young babies on
OL,7,Fthat bus too who were crying in
OL,8,Fdistress, my son being one of them. I
OL,9,Fhad family flying out from Birmingham
OL,10,F.... and they gave them a #3.00 food
OL,11,Fvoucher each.
OL,13,F"They were delayed at least 4/5 hours.
OL,14,FI do want to add that I'm thankful no
OL,15,Fone was seriously harmed in the crash
OL,16,Fand everyone was safe and well.
OL,17,FHopefully my next trip to see my
OL,18,Ffamily abroad is much smoother".
OL,20,F"We've heard nothing"
