OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FIf you still want to travel, your
OL,7,Fairline must find you an alternative
OL,8,Fflight. If another airline is flying
OL,9,Fto your destination significantly
OL,10,Fsooner, or there are other suitable
OL,11,Fmodes of transport available, then you
OL,12,Fhave a right to be booked onto that
OL,13,Falternative transport instead.
OL,15,FAccording to the Civil Aviation
OL,16,FAuthority (CAA), an airline must
OL,17,Fprovide a reasonable amount of food
OL,18,Fand drink in the case of a
OL,19,F"significant delay".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/16
