OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhat is classed as a significant delay?
OL,13,FThis usually comes in the form of
OL,14,Fvouchers, but if an airline cannot
OL,15,Fprovide food and drink or voucher
OL,16,Fequivalent for whatever reason,
OL,17,Fcustomers can make their own
OL,18,F"reasonable" arrangements and keep
OL,19,Ftheir receipts to claim the money back.
