OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FThis can include not just food and
OL,7,Fdrink, but also the cost of calls,
OL,8,Faccommodation and transport to a hotel
OL,9,For home. The CAA adds that "luxury
OL,10,Fhotels and alcohol" are unlikely to be
OL,11,Fcovered.
OL,13,FCan I claim compensation?
OL,15,FAirlines are required to pay
OL,16,Fcompensation if flights arrive more
OL,17,Fthan three hours late, but only when
OL,18,Fit is deemed to be within their
OL,19,Fcontrol.
