OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FFor example, a fault with the aircraft
OL,7,For pilot sickness.
OL,9,FCauses of disruption classed as
OL,10,Foutside their control include severe
OL,11,Fweather, air traffic control
OL,12,Frestrictions and security alerts.
OL,14,FThe amount of compensation you could
OL,15,Fbe due will depend on the length of
OL,16,Fthe flight and how much its arrival
OL,17,Fwas later than scheduled. This works
OL,18,Fout as follows:
OL,20,F"They've got to get you to your
OL,21,Fdestination as soon as they can"
