OL,3,CBirmingham Airport disruption: What if
OL,4,Cyour flight is delayed or cancelled?
OL,6,FTravel expert Simon Calder told ITV
OL,7,FNews Central:
OL,9,F"Under air passenger rights rules,
OL,10,Fit's really clear what the airline has
OL,11,Fto do. If your flight is cancelled,
OL,12,Fthey've got to get you to your
OL,13,Fdestination as soon as they can, using
OL,14,Fany airline that has seats available.
